{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "qa-platform-afex",
    "name": "QA Platform AFEX",
    "description": "## Setup rápido (2 pasos)\n\n**1. Agrega en tu `.env.local`:**\n```\nAPI_KEY=mi-clave-secreta-aqui\n```\nReinicia el servidor.\n\n**2. En Postman:**\n- Ve a la colección → Edit → Variables\n- Pon tu clave en `apiKey`\n- ¡Listo! Todos los requests se autenticarán automáticamente.\n\n---\n\n## Sobre los IDs en las respuestas\n\nCada registro tiene dos identificadores:\n- **`id`** → ID interno de la BD (cuid). Se usa en las URLs de los endpoints.\n- **`jiraTask` / `caseId`** → Identificador legible (ej: `CCUM-5802`, `TC-001`). Es lo que reconoces.\n\nEjemplo de respuesta:\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"cmm9ozee40001wy8g2ayhiybe\",   ← usa este en las URLs\n  \"jiraTask\": \"CCUM-5802\",              ← este es el que ves en JIRA\n  \"caseId\": \"TC-001\"                    ← identificador del escenario\n}\n```\n\nLos scripts de Test de cada request guardan el `id` automáticamente en `{{testPlanId}}` / `{{testCaseId}}`.\n\n## Trazabilidad en Network tab\nTodos los requests que hace la app son visibles en:\nChrome DevTools → **Network** → Filtrar por **Fetch/XHR**",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Agrega automáticamente el Bearer token a todos los requests",
          "const apiKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('apiKey');",
          "if (apiKey) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.upsert({",
          "    key: 'Authorization',",
          "    value: 'Bearer ' + apiKey",
          "  });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiKey",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Valor de API_KEY definido en .env.local"
    },
    {
      "key": "testPlanId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Se rellena automáticamente al crear un Caso de Prueba"
    },
    {
      "key": "testCaseId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Se rellena automáticamente al crear un Escenario"
    },
    {
      "key": "celulaId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "developerId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "qaId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth (solo sin apiKey)",
      "description": "Solo necesitas esto si no usas API_KEY. Con apiKey configurado, sáltate esta sección.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Obtener CSRF Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.csrfToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('csrfToken', res.csrfToken);",
                  "  console.log('csrfToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/csrf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "csrf"]
            },
            "description": "Ejecuta primero para obtener el csrfToken necesario en el Login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "csrfToken", "value": "{{csrfToken}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "email", "value": "admin@afex.com", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "Admin123!", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "callbackUrl", "value": "/dashboard", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "json", "value": "true", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/callback/credentials",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "callback", "credentials"]
            },
            "description": "NextAuth guarda la cookie de sesión automáticamente en Postman."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verificar sesión activa",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "session"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Casos de Prueba (Test Plans)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar Casos de Prueba",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/casos?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "casos"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "status", "value": "IN_PROGRESS", "disabled": true, "description": "CREATED | IN_PROGRESS | COMPLETED | CANCELLED" },
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "Busca por jiraTask o descripción" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener Caso de Prueba (por id interno)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/casos/{{testPlanId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "casos", "{{testPlanId}}"],
              "description": "Usa {{testPlanId}} que se guarda automáticamente al crear un caso."
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear Caso de Prueba",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.success && res.data) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('testPlanId', res.data.id);",
                  "  console.log('✅ testPlanId:', res.data.id, '| jiraTask:', res.data.jiraTask);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jiraTask\": \"AFEX-9999\",\n  \"description\": \"Descripción del caso de prueba\",\n  \"epic\": \"AFEX-EPIC-001\",\n  \"celulaId\": \"{{celulaId}}\",\n  \"developerId\": \"{{developerId}}\",\n  \"qaId\": \"{{qaId}}\",\n  \"relatedJiraTasks\": [\"AFEX-1000\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/casos",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "casos"]
            },
            "description": "El ID interno del plan creado se guarda automáticamente en {{testPlanId}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Caso de Prueba",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jiraTask\": \"AFEX-9999\",\n  \"description\": \"Descripción actualizada\",\n  \"epic\": \"AFEX-EPIC-002\",\n  \"status\": \"IN_PROGRESS\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/casos/{{testPlanId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "casos", "{{testPlanId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar Caso de Prueba",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/casos/{{testPlanId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "casos", "{{testPlanId}}"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
