    "_postman_id": "qa-platform-afex",
    "name": "QA Platform AFEX",
    "description": "Colección de endpoints para la plataforma QA AFEX.\n\n**Setup inicial:**\n1. Ejecuta `POST /auth/login` con tus credenciales\n2. La variable `{{token}}` se guarda automáticamente en las cookies de sesión de NextAuth (jwt)\n3. Todos los demás endpoints requieren tener la cookie de sesión activa\n\n**Variables de entorno:**\n- `baseUrl`: http://localhost:3000",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "testPlanId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "testCaseId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "celulaId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "developerId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "qaId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// La cookie de sesión se guarda automáticamente en Postman",
                  "pm.test('Login exitoso', function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"csrfToken\": \"\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@afex.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\",\n  \"callbackUrl\": \"/dashboard\",\n  \"json\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/callback/credentials",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "callback", "credentials"]
            },
            "description": "Inicia sesión. NextAuth guarda la cookie de sesión automáticamente."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Session",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "session"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica la sesión activa."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get CSRF Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/csrf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "csrf"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene el token CSRF necesario para el login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nuevo Usuario\",\n  \"email\": \"nuevo@afex.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\",\n  \"role\": \"QA\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
